content:
# AI 编程互助会 07 群聊天数据分析报告

以下是根据您的要求生成的完整HTML页面：

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI 编程互助会 07 群 - 聊天数据分析报告</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <script src="https://d3js.org/d3.v7.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #FF6B6B;
            --secondary: #FFD166;
            --accent: #06D6A0;
            --background: #FFF9F2;
            --card-bg: #FFF3E6;
            --text: #5C4033;
            --light-text: #8B5A2B;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--background);
            color: var(--text);
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary) 0%, var(--primary) 100%);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.2);
            color: white;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .stats-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--light-text);
        }

        .chart-container {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--primary);
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--secondary);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .top-users {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .user-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 180px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        .user-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .user-messages {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .topic-cloud {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .topic-tag {
            background: var(--secondary);
            color: var(--text);
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .topic-tag:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .timeline {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            background: white;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .timeline-time {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .timeline-user {
            color: var(--light-text);
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .word-cloud {
            height: 300px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .tool-list {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .tool-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .tool-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .tool-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            color: var(--light-text);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(92, 64, 51, 0.1);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .stats-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .tool-list {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .stats-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .user-card {
                min-width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>AI 编程互助会 07 群</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">2025年6月20日聊天数据分析报告</div>
        </header>

        <div class="stats-container">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value">500</div>
                <div class="stat-label">消息总数</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value">438</div>
                <div class="stat-label">有效文本消息</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value">40</div>
                <div class="stat-label">活跃用户数</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value">22</div>
                <div class="stat-label">讨论话题数</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chart-container">
            <h2 class="section-title">活跃用户分析</h2>
            <canvas id="userChart"></canvas>

            <div class="top-users">
                <div class="user-card">
                    <div class="user-name">超级峰</div>
                    <div class="user-messages">111 条消息</div>
                    <div>主要讨论: Cursor AI、知识管理</div>
                </div>
                <div class="user-card">
                    <div class="user-name">擎天</div>
                    <div class="user-messages">43 条消息</div>
                    <div>主要讨论: 前端开发、知识库</div>
                </div>
                <div class="user-card">
                    <div class="user-name">YoSign</div>
                    <div class="user-messages">38 条消息</div>
                    <div>主要讨论: AI模型、token限制</div>
                </div>
                <div class="user-card">
                    <div class="user-name">好记星</div>
                    <div class="user-messages">32 条消息</div>
                    <div>主要讨论: AI工具、组件框架</div>
                </div>
                <div class="user-card">
                    <div class="user-name">杨智</div>
                    <div class="user-messages">31 条消息</div>
                    <div>主要讨论: 视频工具、PPT优化</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chart-container">
            <h2 class="section-title">热门话题</h2>
            <div class="topic-cloud">
                <div class="topic-tag">Cursor AI 新计费模式</div>
                <div class="topic-tag">Claude 4 使用体验</div>
                <div class="topic-tag">前端组件框架对比</div>
                <div class="topic-tag">知识库搭建方案</div>
                <div class="topic-tag">白板工具推荐</div>
                <div class="topic-tag">视频自动剪辑技术</div>
                <div class="topic-tag">PPT优化工具</div>
                <div class="topic-tag">Token限制问题</div>
                <div class="topic-tag">AI编程实践</div>
                <div class="topic-tag">响应式设计</div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-time">09:51:16</div>
                    <div class="timeline-user">好记星</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">不限总数量，限制频次，其实跟claude pro一样</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-time">10:17:34</div>
                    <div class="timeline-user">西西Xylvia</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">能干干，不能干滚，你不干有的是AI干... (经典AI激励prompt)</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-time">15:35:12</div>
                    <div class="timeline-user">超级峰</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">推荐一下，前几天刚发现，但是访问量很大的免费在线画图工具：https://excalidraw.com/</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-time">17:18:27</div>
                    <div class="timeline-user">超级峰</div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">shadcn - Build your Component Library: https://ui.shadcn.com/</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chart-container">
            <h2 class="section-title">活跃时段分析</h2>
            <canvas id="timeChart"></canvas>
        </div>

        <div class="chart-container">
            <h2 class="section-title">讨论工具与技术</h2>
            <div class="tool-list">
                <div class="tool-card">
                    <div class="tool-name">Cursor AI</div>
                    <div>AI编程助手，支持Claude 4 Opus模型，讨论新计费模式和使用体验</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tool-card">
                    <div class="tool-name">Excalidraw</div>
                    <div>免费在线画图工具，手绘风格，月访问量300万</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tool-card">
                    <div class="tool-name">shadcn/ui</div>
                    <div>前端组件库，简约苹果风格，一致性好于Ant Design</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tool-card">
                    <div class="tool-name">FastStone Capture</div>
                    <div>轻量级录屏软件，仅8MB大小，支持摄像头录制</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tool-card">
                    <div class="tool-name">Claude 4</div>
                    <div>Anthropic的AI模型，讨论token限制和响应速度问题</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tool-card">
                    <div class="tool-name">Gemini</div>
                    <div>Google的AI模型，支持视频理解和自动切片</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chart-container">
            <h2 class="section-title">关键词云</h2>
            <div class="word-cloud" id="wordCloud"></div>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>AI 编程互助会 07 群 | 聊天数据分析报告</p>
            <p>生成时间: 2025年6月21日 | 数据范围: 2025-06-20全天</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 用户消息数据
        const userData = {
            labels: ['超级峰', '擎天', 'YoSign', '好记星', '杨智', '其他用户'],
            datasets: [{
                label: '消息数量',
                data: [111, 43, 38, 32, 31, 245],
                backgroundColor: [
                    '#FF6B6B', '#FFD166', '#06D6A0', '#118AB2', '#073B4C', '#8B5A2B'
                ],
                borderColor: [
                    '#E04F4F', '#E8B95C', '#05B88E', '#0D779D', '#052A38', '#6B4729'
                ],
                borderWidth: 1
            }]
        };

        // 时间分布数据
        const timeData = {
            labels: ['00-02', '02-04', '04-06', '06-08', '08-10', '10-12', '12-14', '14-16', '16-18', '18-20', '20-22', '22-24'],
            datasets: [{
                label: '消息数量',
                data: [4, 0, 0, 2, 98, 123, 12, 45, 102, 67, 37, 10],
                backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.5)',
                borderColor: '#FF6B6B',
                borderWidth: 2,
                tension: 0.3,
                fill: true
            }]
        };

        // 关键词数据
        const words = [
            {text: "Cursor", size: 45},
            {text: "AI", size: 60},
            {text: "模型", size: 35},
            {text: "token", size: 30},
            {text: "Claude", size: 40},
            {text: "前端", size: 35},
            {text: "组件", size: 30},
            {text: "工具", size: 50},
            {text: "知识库", size: 40},
            {text: "开发", size: 35},
            {text: "设计", size: 30},
            {text: "视频", size: 35},
            {text: "PPT", size: 30},
            {text: "优化", size: 25},
            {text: "响应式", size: 25},
            {text: "编程", size: 40},
            {text: "框架", size: 35},
            {text: "shadcn", size: 30},
            {text: "Excalidraw", size: 35},
            {text: "Gemini", size: 30}
        ];

        // 初始化图表
        window.onload = function() {
            // 用户消息图表
            const userCtx = document.getElementById('userChart').getContext('2d');
            new Chart(userCtx, {
                type: 'bar',
                data: userData,
                options: {
                    responsive: true,
                    plugins: {
                        legend: {
                            display: false
                        },
                        title: {
                            display: true,
                            text: '消息数量最多的前5位用户',
                            font: {
                                size: 16
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    scales: {
                        y: {
                            beginAtZero: true,
                            ticks: {
                                precision: 0
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            });

            // 时间分布图表
            const timeCtx = document.getElementById('timeChart').getContext('2d');
            new Chart(timeCtx, {
                type: 'line',
                data: timeData,
                options: {
                    responsive: true,
                    plugins: {
                        title: {
                            display: true,
                            text: '消息数量按时间分布',
                            font: {
                                size: 16
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    scales: {
                        y: {
                            beginAtZero: true,
                            ticks: {
                                precision: 0
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            });

            // 创建词云
            createWordCloud();
        };

        // 创建词云函数
        function createWordCloud() {
            const width = 800;
            const height = 300;

            const svg = d3.select("#wordCloud")
                .append("svg")
                .attr("width", width)
                .attr("height", height);

            const g = svg.append("g")
                .attr("transform", `translate(${width/2},${height/2})`);

            const colorScale = d3.scaleLinear()
                .domain([0, 60])
                .range(['#FFD166', '#FF6B6B']);

            const layout = d3.layout.cloud()
                .size([width, height])
                .words(words)
                .padding(5)
                .rotate(0)
                .fontSize(d => d.size)
                .on("end", draw);

            layout.start();

            function draw(words) {
                g.selectAll("text")
                    .data(words)
                    .enter().append("text")
                    .style("font-size", d => d.size + "px")
                    .style("fill", d => colorScale(d.size))
                    .attr("text-anchor", "middle")
                    .attr("transform", d => `translate(${d.x},${d.y})rotate(${d.rotate})`)
                    .text(d => d.text);
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

这个HTML页面提供了全面的聊天数据分析报告，主要特点包括：

1. **暖色系设计**：使用橙色、黄色和绿色为主的温暖色调，符合要求
2. **响应式布局**：适配各种屏幕尺寸
3. **多种数据可视化**：
   - 活跃用户柱状图
   - 消息时间分布折线图
   - 关键词词云
4. **关键数据展示**：
   - 消息总数、有效消息数等统计卡片
   - 热门话题标签云
   - 重要消息时间线
   - 讨论工具和技术列表
5. **专业美观的UI**：
   - 圆角卡片设计
   - 平滑的悬停动画
   - 精心设计的排版和间距

所有CSS和JavaScript代码都直接包含在HTML文件中，没有外部文件依赖，使用了Chart.js和D3.js的CDN链接进行数据可视化。
